    <item>
      <title>由于担心负资产，亨特放弃了对英国购房者的帮助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/hunt-ditched-help-for-uk-homebuyers-on-negative-equity-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特曾考虑在上周的预算中为首次购房者提供更多帮助，但由于担心房价可能进一步下跌，因此没有这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/hunt-ditched-help-for-uk-homebuyers-on-negative-equity-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:32:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国表示，在全球稳定面临的风险中，富国正在将穷人抛在后面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/rich-nations-leaving-poor-behind-in-risk-to-global-stability-un-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国表示，衡量人们生活质量和寿命的指标提供了富国和穷国之间日益扩大的分歧的新证据，并警告说，全球不平等现象的扩大有可能引发两极分化和僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/rich-nations-leaving-poor-behind-in-risk-to-global-stability-un-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟协议陷入僵局，巴西着眼于向印度和非洲出口农产品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/brazil-eyes-farm-exports-to-india-and-africa-with-eu-deal-stuck</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦希望扩大对印度和非洲的农产品出口，在南美贸易集团与欧盟之间的贸易谈判陷入困境之际，更多地关注新市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/brazil-eyes-farm-exports-to-india-and-africa-with-eu-deal-stuck</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 15:48:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰夫·亚斯 (Jeff Yass) 在 TikTok 上的 150 亿美元财富彰显了他的共和党影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/who-is-jeff-yass-15-billion-tiktok-fortune-at-stake-as-ban-passes-house-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着一些对 TikTok 最严厉的共和党批评者软化了对这款中国支持的社交媒体应用程序的立场，一位亿万富翁捐赠者的名字在华盛顿传开了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/who-is-jeff-yass-15-billion-tiktok-fortune-at-stake-as-ban-passes-house-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 15:13:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特称保守党捐助者的言论是种族主义，但道歉应该被接受</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/hunt-says-tory-donor-comments-racist-apology-should-be-accepted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特表示，一位保守党高级捐助者的言论是“种族主义”和“卑鄙”，但该人已经表示悔恨，道歉应该被接受。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/hunt-says-tory-donor-comments-racist-apology-should-be-accepted</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 15:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佐治亚州案件中的特朗普法官驳回了对他的一些指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/trump-judge-in-georgia-case-dismisses-some-counts-against-him</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在佐治亚州试图推翻 2020 年总统选举的起诉中取得了部分胜利，法官驳回了针对他和其他被告的几项刑事指控，但庞大的起诉书的大部分内容仍然有效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/trump-judge-in-georgia-case-dismisses-some-counts-against-him</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:25:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克因种族主义争议拒绝退还捐款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/sunak-refuses-to-return-donation-as-racism-row-embroils-tories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)不顾压力，将一名商人向其保守党退还1000万英镑(1280万美元)的捐款，首相谴责这名商人对反对派政客发表“种族主义”言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/sunak-refuses-to-return-donation-as-racism-row-embroils-tories</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前联邦调查局线人被指控亨特·拜登撒谎诱骗银行行长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/ex-fbi-spy-charged-with-hunter-biden-lie-ensnared-a-bank-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这名前联邦调查局线人被指控谎称亨特·拜登从一家乌克兰能源公司收受数百万美元贿赂，他也是美国针对一位著名奥地利银行家的案件背后的间谍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/ex-fbi-spy-charged-with-hunter-biden-lie-ensnared-a-bank-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:03:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国顾问指出习近平推动产业发展存在地缘政治风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/china-adviser-flags-geopolitical-risks-in-xi-s-industry-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位与政府有联系的经济学家表示，中国需要调整其产业政策，以应对美国和欧洲对产能过剩日益增长的批评，这突显出人们越来越意识到阻碍高科技出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/china-adviser-flags-geopolitical-risks-in-xi-s-industry-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 07:17:00 GMT</pubDate>
